426
00:30:09,880 --> 00:30:11,480
Talk to you later.

427
00:30:11,480 --> 00:30:15,890
OK. Call me when you’re… back.

428
00:30:18,120 --> 00:30:19,630
This woman.

429
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:24,980
You don’t want to see my superpower?

430
00:30:44,490 --> 00:30:48,670
How’s it? It’s not like taking a poster photo.

431
00:30:48,670 --> 00:30:52,530
Did your man agree with this?

432
00:30:52,530 --> 00:30:58,400
He’s not promised to marry you yet and
you’re choosing the wedding dress?

433
00:30:58,400 --> 00:31:00,360
He promised with his action.

434
00:31:00,360 --> 00:31:02,000
How?

435
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:05,740
He was about to somewhere far away,

436
00:31:05,740 --> 00:31:07,410
but then he decided to stay for me.

437
00:31:07,410 --> 00:31:08,370
Where was he going?

438
00:31:08,370 --> 00:31:09,980
You don’t need to know about that.

439
00:31:09,980 --> 00:31:12,190
But is it OK if he doesn’t go there?

440
00:31:12,190 --> 00:31:14,550
I think so. Otherwise he won’t stay.

441
00:31:14,550 --> 00:31:20,820
He must have his reason to go there.

442
00:31:20,820 --> 00:31:24,630
Did you forced him to stay with tears,

443
00:31:24,630 --> 00:31:30,740
