444
00:31:30,740 --> 00:31:32,290
You won’t come back?

445
00:31:32,290 --> 00:31:33,420
You’ll just leave for good?

446
00:31:33,420 --> 00:31:35,270
What if you don’t go?

447
00:31:35,270 --> 00:31:36,760
Why must you go now?

448
00:31:36,760 --> 00:31:40,720
You can’t just stay here with me?

449
00:31:42,080 --> 00:31:43,980
Don’t be… silly.

450
00:31:43,980 --> 00:31:46,570
I knew it.

451
00:31:46,570 --> 00:31:50,920
Ask him what will happen if he doesn’t go.

452
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:55,050
Don’t ruin a nice and talented young man.

453
00:31:55,050 --> 00:32:01,540
