456
00:32:20,190 --> 00:32:23,270
Min-joon, we have to talk.

457
00:32:23,270 --> 00:32:24,780
Come in.

458
00:32:29,040 --> 00:32:30,940
I’ll get down to business then.

459
00:32:30,940 --> 00:32:34,240
If it’s you, I’ll agree from my heart.

460
00:32:37,380 --> 00:32:40,940
Well, thank you.

461
00:32:40,940 --> 00:32:42,910
My mom’s tricky.

462
00:32:42,910 --> 00:32:44,960
But I’ll handle this.

463
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:47,950
You can sign a contract, making some promises.

464
00:32:47,950 --> 00:32:51,180
This works well. Very convincing.

465
00:32:51,180 --> 00:32:55,340
Then my mom might agree.

466
00:32:55,340 --> 00:32:57,530
With what?

467
00:32:57,530 --> 00:32:58,900
Your marriage with my sister.

468
00:32:58,900 --> 00:33:00,030
What?

469
00:33:00,030 --> 00:33:02,270
I don’t ask for much.

470
00:33:02,270 --> 00:33:05,380
