480
00:33:40,490 --> 00:33:41,360
I see.

481
00:33:41,360 --> 00:33:44,790
So please, never let her cry.

482
00:33:45,280 --> 00:33:46,630
From this perspective,

483
00:33:46,630 --> 00:33:49,150
I’ll say,

484
00:33:49,750 --> 00:33:50,800
