490
00:34:21,199 --> 00:34:22,400
Excuse me.

491
00:34:23,100 --> 00:34:24,100
Yes?

492
00:34:24,100 --> 00:34:25,270
Can I help you?

493
00:34:25,989 --> 00:34:28,110
Where’s the parking boy?

494
00:34:28,110 --> 00:34:31,940
