497
00:34:36,590 --> 00:34:38,489
Your car looks expensive. If I hit it…

498
00:34:38,489 --> 00:34:41,110
Stop babbling. Just park my car.

499
00:34:41,110 --> 00:34:43,980
You are paid to provide service.

500
00:34:43,980 --> 00:34:45,280
Sir,

501
00:34:45,280 --> 00:34:48,020
