502
00:35:05,130 --> 00:35:06,860
What’s happening?

503
00:35:06,860 --> 00:35:07,660
Honey.

504
00:35:07,660 --> 00:35:10,190
Is the car rampaging?

505
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,570
But no one’s inside.

506
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:25,970
Who are you?

507
00:35:25,970 --> 00:35:29,500
If you can’t even park your car without help,

508
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:33,200
then maybe you should not drive.

509
00:35:33,200 --> 00:35:34,260
What?

510
00:35:35,570 --> 00:35:38,350
I meet a nasty man today.

511
00:35:50,590 --> 00:35:53,330
