526
00:36:55,510 --> 00:36:57,140
How stupid I was!

527
00:36:57,720 --> 00:37:01,290
I should’ve been with them despite my failure.

528
00:37:01,640 --> 00:37:04,090
I should’ve been with them.

529
00:37:04,730 --> 00:37:06,420
It’s been years,

