00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:01,520
Oh gosh!

557
00:39:02,900 --> 00:39:05,470
Why did you?

558
00:39:05,470 --> 00:39:06,940
Get away.

559
00:39:07,290 --> 00:39:09,870
Don’t treat him like this.

560
00:39:09,870 --> 00:39:10,730
What?

561
00:39:10,730 --> 00:39:12,070
Don’t ask.

562
00:39:12,070 --> 00:39:13,750
I won’t tell you anything.

563
00:39:14,280 --> 00:39:15,520
Min-joon.

564
00:39:54,130 --> 00:39:55,400
Shush.

565
00:39:56,610 --> 00:39:58,700
Yun-jae, that was…

566
00:40:01,440 --> 00:40:03,260
I’ll keep your secret.

567
00:40:03,260 --> 00:40:04,620
I promise.

568
00:40:05,570 --> 00:40:07,260
Well.

569
00:40:07,260 --> 00:40:08,460
OK.

570
00:40:10,480 --> 00:40:11,410
Thank you.

571
00:40:11,410 --> 00:40:13,660
Can I ask you a favor?

572
00:40:19,750 --> 00:40:21,310
What do you want?

573
00:40:26,520 --> 00:40:28,380
You’ve mistaken me.

574
00:40:29,070 --> 00:40:31,110
I don’t do that…

575
00:40:31,110 --> 00:40:32,370
Good.

576
00:41:01,010 --> 00:41:01,930
How is it?

577
00:41:01,930 --> 00:41:03,220
How is it?

578
00:41:05,350 --> 00:41:07,900
Don’t make soup anymore.

579
00:41:15,110 --> 00:41:16,700
I’ve got a question.

580
00:41:16,700 --> 00:41:18,700
How much is the management fee here?

581
00:41:20,720 --> 00:41:21,670
Why?

582
00:41:23,060 --> 00:41:25,070
Maybe it’s because it’s winter now,

583
00:41:25,070 --> 00:41:28,670
the electricity and gas charges are very high.

584
00:41:28,670 --> 00:41:31,970
I heard that there is a progressive
tax on electricity recently.

585
00:41:31,970 --> 00:41:34,020
The cost is very high.

586
00:41:34,020 --> 00:41:36,130
And I rent this house on a monthly basis.

587
00:41:36,130 --> 00:41:41,330
The management fee, the rent… They cost a lot.

588
00:41:47,300 --> 00:41:49,880
You’re… desperate for money?

589
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:52,480
No, that’s not what I mean.

590
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:53,740
You live next door to me.

591
00:41:53,740 --> 00:41:56,220
And we often have meals together. At night we…

592
00:41:56,220 --> 00:41:58,550
You know what I mean.

593
00:41:58,550 --> 00:42:00,680
The management fee and rent…

594
00:42:00,680 --> 00:42:03,940
That’s a waste of money.

595
00:42:03,940 --> 00:42:06,590
What? Can you just make it clear?

596
00:42:06,590 --> 00:42:07,160
Forget it.

597
00:42:07,160 --> 00:42:08,480
Never mind.

598
00:42:12,820 --> 00:42:15,140
Let’s go there tonight.

599
00:42:15,140 --> 00:42:16,300
What?

600
00:42:16,300 --> 00:42:17,520
Where?

601
00:42:18,370 --> 00:42:20,060
Namsan Tower

602
00:42:21,270 --> 00:42:22,530
I thought you want to go.

603
00:42:24,530 --> 00:42:25,790
Sure.

604
00:42:28,440 --> 00:42:30,800
I’ll dress up for that.

605
00:42:30,800 --> 00:42:33,870
And you should dress up too.

606
00:42:34,190 --> 00:42:36,630
Why make a fuss?

607
00:42:52,650 --> 00:42:54,360
She’s in my room.

608
00:42:54,360 --> 00:42:56,630
She had some porridge in the morning.

609
00:42:56,630 --> 00:43:00,900
Sorry for always bothering you.

610
00:43:00,900 --> 00:43:02,520
Don’t be.

611
00:43:02,520 --> 00:43:06,420
A keen prosecutor’s protecting his witness.

612
00:43:07,290 --> 00:43:08,720
You’ve done nothing wrong.

613
00:43:08,720 --> 00:43:10,560
Don’t be sorry.

614
00:43:16,850 --> 00:43:23,470
I felt weird after marrying Jae-kyung.

615
00:43:23,470 --> 00:43:26,700
He was perfect in front of others.

616
00:43:26,700 --> 00:43:29,570
But to me, he seemed to be hiding something.

617
00:43:30,520 --> 00:43:31,700
Then

618
00:43:32,440 --> 00:43:34,050
one day,

619
00:43:34,310 --> 00:43:37,880
I accidentally found something I should not see.

620
00:43:38,770 --> 00:43:41,120
I found a recorder

621
00:43:41,120 --> 00:43:43,750
in late Han-kyung’s home

622
00:43:44,610 --> 00:43:49,360
What’s in the recorder?

623
00:43:53,190 --> 00:43:58,470
Anything about Han-kyung?

624
00:43:58,880 --> 00:44:01,900
Jae-kyung knew nothing about it.

625
00:44:01,900 --> 00:44:06,110
I didn’t want him to know.
So I kept it elsewhere.

626
00:44:07,240 --> 00:44:10,050
I should’ve called the police at that time.

627
00:44:10,990 --> 00:44:12,770
It’s all my fault.

628
00:44:12,770 --> 00:44:14,670
I was terrified.

629
00:44:16,270 --> 00:44:17,880
Where is

630
00:44:20,410 --> 00:44:21,530
the recorder?

631
00:44:21,970 --> 00:44:26,160
[Pawn-broker]

632
00:44:51,660 --> 00:44:54,820
February 23, 2002.

633
00:44:54,820 --> 00:44:57,490
Chaired a leaders’ meeting in the morning.

634
00:44:57,490 --> 00:45:01,100
Afternoon, I went to the store
for Hee-kyung’s graduation gift.

635
00:45:01,670 --> 00:45:07,170
In the evening, Jae-kyung asked to talk
and we decided to drive out.

636
00:45:12,590 --> 00:45:14,340
Han-kyung, have some juice.

637
00:45:15,170 --> 00:45:16,800
Jae-kyung prepared it for you.

638
00:45:16,800 --> 00:45:19,920
Wow, thank you.

639
00:45:19,920 --> 00:45:22,160
I’m going out to meet my friend.

640
00:45:22,160 --> 00:45:24,270
Dad and mom will also be back late tonight.

641
00:45:24,270 --> 00:45:25,130
Is that so?

642
00:45:25,130 --> 00:45:26,820
I will also go out with Jae-kyung later.

643
00:45:26,820 --> 00:45:28,410
Then no one will be home tonight.

644
00:45:31,820 --> 00:45:32,940
Han-kyung,

645
00:45:32,940 --> 00:45:34,190
let’s go.

646
00:45:34,890 --> 00:45:36,390
Jae-kyung,

647
00:45:37,620 --> 00:45:42,130
I’m not feeling well for a while.

648
00:45:42,130 --> 00:45:43,360
What’s wrong?

649
00:45:47,340 --> 00:45:49,350
No idea.

650
00:45:50,520 --> 00:45:52,060
Why do I…

651
00:45:52,840 --> 00:45:56,150
feel drunk?

652
00:45:58,520 --> 00:46:01,190
You’re not drunk.

653
00:46:01,190 --> 00:46:03,300
You’re feeling numb.

654
00:46:05,200 --> 00:46:06,150
What?

655
00:46:06,150 --> 00:46:08,580
You will feel feeble soon.

656
00:46:09,510 --> 00:46:11,670
Unable to walk.

657
00:46:12,450 --> 00:46:14,320
Short of breath.

658
00:46:15,290 --> 00:46:17,070
Tongue paralyzed.

659
00:46:17,640 --> 00:46:19,710
Then you’ll fall asleep deeply.

660
00:46:23,930 --> 00:46:26,270
What… are you talking about?

661
00:46:26,270 --> 00:46:29,170
You’ll be found in the middle of an express way,

662
00:46:29,970 --> 00:46:32,710
dying of DUI.

663
00:46:32,710 --> 00:46:34,370
Jae-kyung…

664
00:46:35,760 --> 00:46:38,900
I always want you to disappear.

665
00:46:41,420 --> 00:46:43,440
You get in my way.

666
00:46:45,200 --> 00:46:52,120
I don’t have any chance because I was younger.

667
00:47:05,440 --> 00:47:06,900
Save me, Jae-kyung.

668
00:47:52,150 --> 00:47:55,590
Open the car boot.

669
00:47:56,730 --> 00:47:58,080
What?

670
00:48:00,660 --> 00:48:02,370
The car boot.

671
00:48:05,180 --> 00:48:06,860
OK.

672
00:48:27,210 --> 00:48:28,710
Is there a brush?

673
00:48:29,820 --> 00:48:31,550
Hand it to me.

674
00:48:42,280 --> 00:48:44,500
Are your arms or legs broken?

675
00:48:44,500 --> 00:48:47,900
Why need me when you have the superpower?

676
00:48:48,280 --> 00:48:49,710
Get in the car.

677
00:49:01,950 --> 00:49:03,070
That’s Cheon Soon-yi, right?

678
00:49:03,070 --> 00:49:04,660
Is that her boyfriend?

679
00:49:08,540 --> 00:49:09,900
Why are you standing there?

680
00:49:10,740 --> 00:49:12,150
Come here.

681
00:49:13,100 --> 00:49:15,880
This is a must for every new couple.

682
00:49:15,880 --> 00:49:17,260
I don’t get it.

683
00:49:17,260 --> 00:49:19,140
This is childish.

684
00:49:20,340 --> 00:49:21,770
Lock it up.

685
00:49:23,160 --> 00:49:24,190
Here.

686
00:49:24,190 --> 00:49:25,700
Come here.

687
00:49:28,600 --> 00:49:29,970
Throw it inside.

688
00:49:31,450 --> 00:49:33,110
Then how can I unlock it?

689
00:49:33,110 --> 00:49:34,950
No one wants to unlock it.

690
00:49:34,950 --> 00:49:37,630
We need to lock our destiny together.

691
00:49:37,630 --> 00:49:39,480
So that we’ll never be apart.

692
00:49:39,480 --> 00:49:41,560
We’ll be each other’s belonging and chain.

693
00:49:41,560 --> 00:49:43,210
That’s the whole point.

694
00:49:50,080 --> 00:49:51,400
There you go.

695
00:49:51,400 --> 00:49:54,940
Do Min-joon. I’ve locked you up.

696
00:49:55,350 --> 00:49:57,320
We are bound together.

697
00:49:59,280 --> 00:50:01,610
You don’t seem to be happy?

698
00:50:01,800 --> 00:50:02,650
No.

699
00:50:02,650 --> 00:50:04,250
I’m happy.

700
00:50:04,960 --> 00:50:07,240
Hey, I’m Cheon Soon-yi.

701
00:50:07,240 --> 00:50:09,740
You’ve been too calm.

702
00:50:09,740 --> 00:50:11,300
And I’m not satisfied with that.

703
00:50:11,300 --> 00:50:13,550
Be more active, will you?

704
00:50:31,990 --> 00:50:33,370
My god.

705
00:50:34,520 --> 00:50:36,100
Here.

706
00:50:37,210 --> 00:50:39,360
My god. Darling.

707
00:50:40,740 --> 00:50:42,370
I’m so touched.

708
00:50:42,370 --> 00:50:43,340
You like it?

709
00:50:43,340 --> 00:50:44,720
Yes.

710
00:50:45,610 --> 00:50:47,110
Ice cream.

711
00:50:49,290 --> 00:50:50,570
Ah.

712
00:50:53,810 --> 00:50:55,100
Darling,

713
00:50:55,100 --> 00:50:56,590
try this on.

714
00:50:58,100 --> 00:51:00,830
Fits me right.

715
00:51:00,830 --> 00:51:02,110
Looks good on me?

716
00:51:02,110 --> 00:51:03,270
Yes.

717
00:51:03,270 --> 00:51:04,900
I love you, darling.

718
00:51:04,900 --> 00:51:06,720
-Fantastic.
-What can I help you?

719
00:51:10,280 --> 00:51:12,050
Do you have ice water?

720
00:51:12,050 --> 00:51:13,380
Yes.

721
00:51:17,550 --> 00:51:19,020
You finish?

722
00:51:19,850 --> 00:51:20,800
Not yet.

723
00:51:20,800 --> 00:51:22,650
Finish the rest and we’ll leave.

724
00:51:35,360 --> 00:51:37,870
What bothers you?

725
00:51:38,260 --> 00:51:39,500
Nothing.

726
00:51:39,500 --> 00:51:41,810
We’ve done the lock thing and had dinner.

727
00:51:41,810 --> 00:51:43,980
Nothing bothers me.

728
00:51:47,240 --> 00:51:48,600
Cheon Soon-yi.

729
00:51:49,710 --> 00:51:51,060
What?

730
00:51:57,020 --> 00:51:58,430
Hello?

731
00:52:01,650 --> 00:52:02,810
OK

732
00:52:02,810 --> 00:52:04,210
I’ll be there soon.

733
00:52:05,970 --> 00:52:07,210
Who’s that?

734
00:52:07,580 --> 00:52:09,040
Something happened.

735
00:52:09,040 --> 00:52:10,590
You go home first.

736
00:52:19,250 --> 00:52:20,750
Alone?

737
00:52:21,150 --> 00:52:22,650
Go home first.

738
00:52:22,650 --> 00:52:24,070
Not your home.

739
00:52:24,470 --> 00:52:25,970
Our home.

740
00:52:26,390 --> 00:52:28,270
Our home?

741
00:52:28,870 --> 00:52:30,710
You mean your home?

742
00:52:31,110 --> 00:52:32,320
Right.

743
00:52:32,500 --> 00:52:36,030
There’s something I have to tell you.

744
00:52:36,970 --> 00:52:38,530
I see.

745
00:52:39,720 --> 00:52:40,950
Cheon Soon-yi.

746
00:52:41,390 --> 00:52:42,750
Yes?

747
00:52:44,070 --> 00:52:45,690
I’ll be back soon.

748
00:52:45,690 --> 00:52:47,090
Wait for me.

749
00:52:48,730 --> 00:52:50,270
OK.

750
00:52:50,270 --> 00:52:52,230
I’ll be waiting for you. Come back soon.

751
00:53:46,420 --> 00:53:48,590
A new round of fate has started.

752
00:53:49,130 --> 00:53:51,450
I’ve been waiting for that planet for 400 years.

753
00:53:51,670 --> 00:53:56,280
3 months later I’ll be back to my last planet.

754
00:53:57,780 --> 00:54:00,540
A woman making a scene after drunk.

755
00:54:00,540 --> 00:54:02,590
An arrogant and ignorant woman.

756
00:54:02,590 --> 00:54:04,090
Annoying.

757
00:54:04,710 --> 00:54:08,110
And that’s my neighbor.

758
00:54:10,650 --> 00:54:13,810
There’s someone. I wish she won’t forget me.

759
00:54:14,920 --> 00:54:17,100
Just when I am about to go back.

760
00:54:18,130 --> 00:54:20,290
Why now?

761
00:54:23,960 --> 00:54:27,280
Today, I told Cheon Soon-yi my identity

762
00:54:27,530 --> 00:54:29,660
in order to push her away.

763
00:54:30,490 --> 00:54:33,720
I hope she’ll run away from me,

764
00:54:34,000 --> 00:54:37,210
and she’ll fear me.

765
00:54:37,410 --> 00:54:40,020
If I miss this chance to come back,

766
00:54:40,460 --> 00:54:45,050
I’ll disappear from this planet.

767
00:54:46,100 --> 00:54:49,220
And soon… I’ll die…

768
00:54:51,350 --> 00:54:55,070
Will it be OK if you stay?

769
00:54:56,200 --> 00:54:57,560
It’s OK.

770
00:55:00,280 --> 00:55:03,870
Seriously?

771
00:55:06,700 --> 00:55:12,300
♫ Could I look at you ♫

772
00:55:12,650 --> 00:55:15,220
[And soon… I’ll die…]

773
00:55:13,580 --> 00:55:19,180
♫ Could I say hello with a smile ♫

774
00:55:19,180 --> 00:55:26,900
♫ I turn and stand with stupid expectations ♫

775
00:55:26,900 --> 00:55:34,150
♫ I see you from afar ♫

776
00:55:34,150 --> 00:55:39,500
♫ Your beautiful long hair ♫

777
00:55:40,930 --> 00:55:46,510
♫ and bashful smile ♫

778
00:55:46,510 --> 00:55:53,400
♫ are as always, as always ♫

779
00:55:53,400 --> 00:56:03,500
♫ But the one besides you is no longer me ♫

780
00:56:00,250 --> 00:56:02,650
Are you seeing your seniors?

781
00:56:02,650 --> 00:56:05,730
Or are you having a job interview?

782
00:56:09,160 --> 00:56:11,570
I’m making a proposal.

783
00:56:15,380 --> 00:56:22,010
♫ I hide from you ♫

784
00:56:21,930 --> 00:56:23,380
Cheon Soon-yi.

785
00:56:22,010 --> 00:56:27,860
♫ in the street corner ♫

786
00:56:24,470 --> 00:56:25,990
Ms. Soon-yi

787
00:56:25,990 --> 00:56:27,260
Soon-yi.

788
00:56:27,860 --> 00:56:35,520
♫ With tears, I turn and stand, like a fool ♫

789
00:56:28,870 --> 00:56:31,510
This is… for you.

790
00:56:34,720 --> 00:56:36,440
No way.

791
00:56:35,520 --> 00:56:43,880
♫ Far away, you’re calling my name ♫

792
00:56:36,770 --> 00:56:40,180
Open the car boot.

793
00:56:55,620 --> 00:56:57,030
You finish?

794
00:56:57,750 --> 00:56:58,840
Not yet.

795
00:56:58,840 --> 00:57:00,480
Finish the rest and we’ll leave.

796
00:57:07,720 --> 00:57:09,270
Cheon Soon-yi.

797
00:57:09,940 --> 00:57:14,780
I don’t know how much time I still have.

798
00:57:16,170 --> 00:57:21,390
Maybe I shouldn’t say this,

799
00:57:22,200 --> 00:57:25,530
but I will try my best

800
00:57:26,410 --> 00:57:30,190
to be at your side as long as possible.

801
00:57:30,580 --> 00:57:34,330
I’m not sure how long will that be,

802
00:57:36,500 --> 00:57:44,660
but I will love you with my whole heart.
